W. J. Hawkins, Plaintiff in Error, v. Seaboard Air Line Railway Company, Defendant in Error. A Writ of Error to a Judgment of the Circuit Court within and for the County of Hillsborough. E. S. Hampton, Fred J. Hampton and G. P. McCord, for Plaintiff in Error; Knight, Thompson & Turner, for Defendant in Error.

Writ of Error dismissed on motion of counsel for plaintiff in error.
